I created this side project to:
1. Help OSS developers to add an additional stream of income;
2. Help the customers to reach out to developers.<p>The whole project was inspired by this experiment <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;feross.org&#x2F;funding-experiment-recap&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;feross.org&#x2F;funding-experiment-recap&#x2F;</a>. I &quot;re-invented&quot; the same terminal ads as did Feross previously, with the only difference being that I did not start coding:)<p>If you are targeting the developers, then please sign up and create a campaign, then developers with a large follower count could feature your product on their GitHub profile and earn money when someone visits your site.
